{"tid":2508962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年對未來悲觀 近6成受訪者欲移民外國","createTime":"2021-04-29T06:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:43:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7a36ccb909ee912f74a61fb41221f4c02f537b","tid":2508962,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"在疫情及政治環境夾擊下，本港青少年不免對前景感到悲觀及迷茫。中文大學一項調查發現，受訪青年對未來社會的樂觀程度，10分滿分中僅得2.95分，比2018年數字大跌逾3成，更有近6成人表示願意離開香港，移民到中國以外的地方發展。至於港府近年力推青少年發展的大灣區，調查發現，僅有不足1成受訪青年表示願意到大灣區工作。<br />\n<br />\n獅子會早前委託中大亞太研究所，就「香港青年對未來的看法」進行問卷調查，並成功於今年3月至4月，以問卷形式訪問803位15至30歲香港居民。調查發現，受訪者對自己未來的整體生活發展，以及香港社會未來的樂觀程度均感到悲觀，在10分滿分中，分別僅得4.76及2.95分，比2018年數字下跌2至3成；更有57.5%受訪青年表示，希望離開香港到中國以外地方發展，相比2018年的46.8%增加逾1成。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/E3YUXDBOZNA6HNFPFPKEJCCVVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FE3YUXDBOZNA6HNFPFPKEJCCVVA%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=4ffbabef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FE3YUXDBOZNA6HNFPFPKEJCCVVA%2F&h=d4585450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/E3YUXDBOZNA6HNFPFPKEJCCVVA/</a>"},{"pid":"fdf6248eb712cf2a7a0b5865349b956065b53915","tid":2508962,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"邊有人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4a2f62c419587eee89fa58a9343994a6b5e237","tid":2508962,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fdf6248eb712cf2a7a0b5865349b956065b53915","tid":2508962,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"邊有人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"呃人果個獅子會其中一個分會主席都走左,不過係呃完錢笑住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"